Generate the complete contents of `.cursor/rules/routing-layout.mdc`.

Scope: Applies to `src/App.tsx`, `src/main.tsx`, and `src/pages/**`.

Rules must enforce:
- Standard SPA routing using react-router-dom.
- Clear separation of public vs protected routes.
- Auth redirects that preserve return destination.
- A catch-all 404 route.
- Readable, non-over-abstracted route definitions.

Do not include app-specific routes.

Output only the markdown content of the rule file.
